article_id:2832,category_name:Events,title_name:A Raid Event Revival, Resplendent Refrain, Is Coming Soon!,image_path:,message:<div>The Resplendent Refrain raid event is coming back! This revival will start <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1650607200"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>During this event, you can use co-op play to fight against the shadow-element raid boss.</div><div><br></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/86a7a59da45d7760dfe77febff813977.png"></div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign to participate.</div><div>2. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign in order to play co-op.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1650348000,update_time1644383601